name: Pamela Cowan
what_you_do: The Neuro Change Master Practitioner course focuses on teaching advanced concepts related to the science of Neuro Change and the conscious and unconscious mind, enabling practitioners to guide clients towards transcendent experiences.
who_you_serve: The course is designed for individuals seeking to deepen their understanding of Neuro Change, including coaches, therapists, and professionals in corporate and sports settings.
